------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This library is a re-implementation of, and bundles linguistic data from:

    AlKhalil Morpho Sys 2
    Arabic Language Processing Team (Oujda NLP Team), Université Mohammed
    Premier, Oujda, Morocco.
    Authors: Azzeddine Mazroui, Mohamed Boudchiche, et al.
    https://alkhalil.oujda-nlp-team.net/
    Licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.

The morphological lexicon shipped under `src/data/` (roots, patterns,
formulas, part-of-speech tables, clitics, proper nouns, tool words and corpus
frequency tables) is derived from AlKhalil Morpho Sys 2's resources and remains
under the GPL-3.0. All credit for the underlying linguistic database and
analysis model belongs to the Oujda NLP Team.

If you use this library in academic work, please also cite the original
AlKhalil Morpho Sys 2 publications by the Oujda NLP Team.
